version_description:
Spend enables users to buy, sell, spend, and manage their funds within the Spend App. This update includes minor bug fixes and performance enhancements.

New Features:

Two-Factor In-App Authentication
International Bank Account Support for 118 Countries
Bank Wire Support Worldwide
Spend Visa Virtual Card Support

Spend enables users to buy, sell, spend, and manage their funds within the Spend App. This update includes performance enhancements, minor bug fixes, and the following:
- multi-currency
- new card activation
- iMessage feature
- new login/signup UI
- favorite wallets support
- main portfolio issue

- Update app icon
- Add card badge
- Fix some bugs
